at Dublin Castle to acknowledge their success with the athletes joined by their friends, family and coaches.\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is just over a month since Team Ireland had its most successful ever Olympic Games, bringing home seven medals from Paris.\", \"from\": 531, \"to\": 656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 561, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.937835235544683e-19, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 650, \"end\": 655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999830290563, \"rank\": 1.6970845771981084e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"President and Sabina Higgins today hosted a reception for Ireland's@TeamIrelandOlympians at the@Paris2024Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 674, \"end\": 688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabina_Higgins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sabina Higgins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabina_Higgins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sabina_Higgins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more athttps://t.co/AoEsk8VSDZpic.twitter.com/JTnLJYCoWT  Team Ireland 'well rested' after Olympics  Double Olympic gold medalist Kellie Harrington said that Team Ireland athletes were \\\"in good form\\\" and \\\"well rested\\\" after the Paris games.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 1025, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 915, \"end\": 932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kellie Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.937835235544683e-19, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1013, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999830290563, \"rank\": 1.6970845771981084e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking at the event in Dublin Castle, the 34-year-old said everyone on Team Ireland helped \\\"to lift the nation\\\" with the performances in Paris.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1100, \"end\": 1112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.937835235544683e-19, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999830290563, \"rank\": 1.6970845771981084e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said the occasion today, which included their friends, families and coaches, was a great way for the entire team to get recognition and to celebrate together.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Chief Executive of the Olympic Federation of Ireland, Peter Sherrard, echoed her words, saying it was an opportunity to have everyone together with their families, which had not been possible after the Toyko Olympics because of Covid-19.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\", \"score\": 0.41125780485559144, \"rank\": 0.7062096176070275, \"text\": \"Peter\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\"}, {\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherrard_High_School\", \"score\": 0.9957567039151362, \"rank\": 0.004261378374783714, \"text\": \"Sherrard\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3914\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherrard_High_School\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherrard_High_School\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes, all wearing their Team Ireland green and white tracksuit, said it was emotional to see everyone but welcomed the opportunity to reflect on their achievements.\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.937835235544683e-19, \"text\": \"Team Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sophie Becker, said she relished her time at the games but also described how it can take time to readjust after the \\\"buzz\\\" of it and going back to the calm of daily life.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1755, \"end\": 1768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Becker\", \"score\": 0.9999944927823652, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sophie Becker\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Becker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sophie_Becker\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is, however, enjoying having the time to meet friends again and \\\"doing normal stuff like grocery shopping \\\".\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For many, it is also about considering what they will do next.\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Showjumper Daniel Coyle described his heartbreak in Paris after being \\\"so close to a medal\\\" as he highlighted the challenge of balancing the highs with the lows.\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2106, \"end\": 2116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Show_jumping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Showjumper\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Show_jumping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Show_jumping\"}, {\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999830290563, \"rank\": 1.6970845771981084e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He remains focused on future success and he is already thinking of the next Olympic games in Los Angeles and hopes \\\"to be there again\\\".\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2404, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2362, \"end\": 2373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999997869509, \"rank\": 2.0315596769653377e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fintan McCarthy, a double Olympic gold medalist, is grateful for the platform that this Olympics and Ireland's success has given to rowing and he is looking forward to continuing his achievements on the water.\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2406, \"end\": 2421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fintan McCarthy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fintan_McCarthy\"}, {\"begin\": 2507, \"end\": 2514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999999828378351, \"rank\": 1.7162119582807084e-08, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said more investment in Irish sport was visible in Paris and he hopes this will continue.\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2644, \"end\": 2649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9981827409545636, \"rank\": 0.0013731680527912917, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 2671, \"end\": 2676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999830290563, \"rank\": 1.6970845771981084e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is hopeful, in particular, that athletes \\\"coming up the ladder\\\" will not be forgotten when it comes to financial support.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Minister for Sport Catherine Martin said commitments were being made to increase investment, with a \\u20ac400 million sports infrastructure planned from grassroot level to high performance.\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She told RT\\u00c9 News that by the time the Olympics 2028 takes place in Los Angeles, she believes there will be \\\"a transformation of sport for the better here\\\".\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3179, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3032, \"end\": 3040, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_News_and_Current_Affairs\", \"score\": 0.9356964890387794, \"rank\": 0.061574627460354234, \"text\": \"RT\\u00c9 News\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_News_and_Current_Affairs\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RT\\u00c9_News_and_Current_Affairs\"}, {\"begin\": 3091, \"end\": 3102, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999997869509, \"rank\": 2.0315596769653377e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"T\\u00e1naiste Michael Martin addressed the possibility of more financial support being provided to Irish athletes and he acknowledged it is something that should be examined \\\"into the future\\\".\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3181, \"end\": 3189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanistry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.666983726917563e-17, \"text\": \"T\\u00e1naiste\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanistry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanistry\"}, {\"begin\": 3198, \"end\": 3204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999927687956616, \"rank\": 7.231249565680146e-06, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}, {\"begin\": 3275, \"end\": 3280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9981827409545636, \"rank\": 0.0013731680527912917, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That is certainly something we should look at,\\\" he said responding to athletes' concerns about funding.\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3474, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think where you have a longterm plan and if we can attach funding along a long term plan, then we can get very good results and very good outcomes which then inspires communities and young people to participate in sport at all levels.\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Minister Martin said he hopes that the Government can do more in terms of investing in elite sports and the national sporting bodies and \\\"not just in the budget but in the time ahead\\\".\", \"from\": 3715, \"to\": 3899, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3724, \"end\": 3730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"score\": 0.9999927687956616, \"rank\": 7.231249565680146e-06, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martin_Crane\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 3903, \"to\": 3914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 4005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3940, \"end\": 3963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"score\": 0.9993664851270567, \"rank\": 0.0006339164685885233, \"text\": \"Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raidi\\u00f3_Teilif\\u00eds_\\u00c9ireann\"}, {\"begin\": 3965,